00:10:28.134 --> 00:10:31.135
you know that my such chakra is catching, that this has happening.

00:10:31.249 --> 00:10:33.370
Now you bring it to the subtle point,

00:10:33.461 --> 00:10:36.998
[which] is first of all you have to work on it physically.

00:10:37.134 --> 00:10:38.134
All right?

00:10:38.480 --> 00:10:42.180
To make yourself absolutely clean there are so many ways.

00:10:42.340 --> 00:10:45.761
First and foremost is feeling the vibrations in different hands,

00:10:45.864 --> 00:10:48.698
feeling them, how it works out.  Which is more, which is less,

00:10:48.800 --> 00:10:51.940
how it’s coming. Why is it this thing?

00:10:52.180 --> 00:10:56.429
