00:10:56.497 --> 00:10:58.412
Such and such person!” Beat him with shoes.

00:10:58.606 --> 00:11:00.463
These are all gross things

00:11:00.611 --> 00:11:03.411
and have to be taken away by gross things.

00:11:03.681 --> 00:11:06.581
