00:12:48.548 --> 00:12:50.548
Physically it has to be done.

00:12:50.690 --> 00:12:54.861
It’s an exercise and you cannot be ‘sahaja’ about it, no.

00:12:55.688 --> 00:12:58.033
There is a difference between Me and you,

00:12:58.149 --> 00:12:59.926
