00:13:02.478 --> 00:13:05.584
“Now we are on top of the world!” You should grow,

00:13:05.720 --> 00:13:08.620
evolve in understanding, and respect others,

00:13:09.358 --> 00:13:13.346
that, “No, we have to still rise and still rise and still rise.”

00:13:13.676 --> 00:13:16.620
This is a physical side, means very important.

00:13:16.930 --> 00:13:20.190
Then the second side is our mental side.

00:13:20.363 --> 00:13:23.548
Now mentally also all the time we are

00:13:23.662 --> 00:13:26.129
bombarded with things from all over.

00:13:26.271 --> 00:13:28.896
