00:15:43.130 --> 00:15:44.410
And I am moving.

00:15:44.520 --> 00:15:48.459
If I have to move it on this path, let me be very, very positive.

00:15:48.550 --> 00:15:50.199
So let me move on this way.”

00:15:50.360 --> 00:15:52.565
