00:16:05.482 --> 00:16:07.817
because you are all the intelligent people,

00:16:07.966 --> 00:16:10.573
and brought up with this intelligent atmosphere,

00:16:10.676 --> 00:16:12.176
there are styles I have seen.

00:16:12.336 --> 00:16:14.929
The intelligent styles are very dangerous,

00:16:15.055 --> 00:16:17.492
they are more dangerous than foolish styles.

00:16:17.594 --> 00:16:19.802
The intelligent styles are that

00:16:19.973 --> 00:16:23.173
you take it in such a way that you cheat yourself.

00:16:23.380 --> 00:16:26.076
All the time you start accepting things

00:16:26.190 --> 00:16:27.867
and you start cheating yourself.

00:16:28.020 --> 00:16:32.164
And these ideas get sedimented in your being, gradually.

00:16:32.299 --> 00:16:35.108
And suddenly you find a big thing in your head

00:16:35.245 --> 00:16:37.467
and you say, “Oh, from where this has come in?

00:16:37.550 --> 00:16:39.400
What has happened to me?”

00:16:39.515 --> 00:16:40.759
So be careful!

00:16:40.873 --> 00:16:44.135
Because these sedimentations will be settling down in you,

00:16:44.251 --> 00:16:47.687
gradually. And you have had those habits

00:16:47.800 --> 00:16:50.010
of intelligent way of doing things.

00:16:50.113 --> 00:16:52.843
When you do intelligently? Actually what is intelligent doing,

00:16:52.934 --> 00:16:56.074
so many times, is just to push it upside down

00:16:56.182 --> 00:16:57.862
and bring it inside you.

00:16:57.982 --> 00:17:01.371
You can see this is something so funny but it is so,

00:17:01.452 --> 00:17:04.173
that when you deal with something intelligently

00:17:04.253 --> 00:17:05.986
you know how to escape it,

00:17:06.100 --> 00:17:07.629
and how to avoid it

00:17:07.754 --> 00:17:12.391
and how to make it look different to yourself.

00:17:12.548 --> 00:17:14.826
You yourself, with intelligence,

00:17:15.018 --> 00:17:17.521
deceive yourself and make it look different

00:17:17.612 --> 00:17:19.310
and then you accept that thing,

00:17:19.435 --> 00:17:21.326
and that becomes a part and parcel of you

00:17:21.423 --> 00:17:23.290
and you are not aware of it.

00:17:23.549 --> 00:17:27.569
Isn’t it Gregoire? It’s a common style, so be careful!

00:17:27.740 --> 00:17:31.611
When you start clearing out your Vishuddhi part of it,

00:17:31.713 --> 00:17:35.377
you will be surprised the subtleness will start flowing in you,

00:17:35.547 --> 00:17:39.841
the subtleness will appear before you. The subtleness is a state.

00:17:40.022 --> 00:17:42.437
It is a state of your attention.

00:17:42.710 --> 00:17:44.896
Your attention is gross outside.

00:17:45.010 --> 00:17:47.617
Now you think of some sort of

00:17:47.743 --> 00:17:50.327
a moon which is just a stone you can call it.

00:17:50.476 --> 00:17:54.838
Then it starts little bit moving, becomes little,

00:17:54.942 --> 00:17:59.045
I should say, mobile, then gradually it becomes subtle.

00:17:59.237 --> 00:18:03.044
The core is melting away, the outside is still hard.

00:18:03.181 --> 00:18:06.505
It’s like that is your attention. It starts melting in you.

00:18:06.620 --> 00:18:10.801
Now you are in the core, you are not outside,

00:18:10.949 --> 00:18:12.737
but whenever you come in contact,

00:18:12.859 --> 00:18:15.164
the core part contacts with the gross,

00:18:15.271 --> 00:18:17.397
suddenly you start becoming one with it,

00:18:17.500 --> 00:18:20.710
then the crust starts again becoming

00:18:20.813 --> 00:18:23.704
an immobile stuff and the core starts becoming strong.

00:18:23.806 --> 00:18:25.674
Again you increase the core,

00:18:25.788 --> 00:18:28.973
it starts again to go out to periphery and the things stars melting

00:18:29.109 --> 00:18:31.730
That is how the attention, if you can understand, is.

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:34.299
And that attention, which is enlightened in you,

00:18:34.390 --> 00:18:36.646
has to be kept all the time enlightened:

00:18:36.725 --> 00:18:38.556
no justification with yourself!

00:18:38.693 --> 00:18:41.529
With others also we don't have to justify.

00:18:41.655 --> 00:18:42.855
It’s all right.

00:18:43.178 --> 00:18:46.327
We think that we must grow, we must be all right,

00:18:46.452 --> 00:18:50.690
we must be very good and when we find somebody is troubling us,

00:18:50.803 --> 00:18:54.782
it’s rather difficult to tolerate a nonsense like that, it’s true.

00:18:54.900 --> 00:18:57.664
But, for that, I am sitting down, you just tell me

00:18:57.789 --> 00:18:59.874
and I can manage it! You have seen

00:18:59.954 --> 00:19:01.957
[how] we have solved one problem very nicely,

00:19:02.036 --> 00:19:03.654
and we can solve all the problems.

00:19:03.753 --> 00:19:06.335
It’s a very clever way, isn't it? That the subtle way!

00:19:06.460 --> 00:19:08.060
It just gets solved!

00:19:08.232 --> 00:19:10.656
So we don’t have to worry about anything.

00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:13.037
You don’t have to think a 100 times!

00:19:13.138 --> 00:19:15.368
Though I am the person who has put you in problems you see,

00:19:15.473 --> 00:19:17.580
“Do like this! You should have done like this!

00:19:17.659 --> 00:19:19.631
You should have put in effort like this!”

00:19:19.713 --> 00:19:21.763
But the problem I will be solving myself, you see.

00:19:21.867 --> 00:19:24.464
But I will just make you run up and down to see that.

00:19:24.541 --> 00:19:27.305
On the contrary when you see me doing like that

00:19:27.376 --> 00:19:29.659
you should understand I am I am playing tricks with you!

00:19:29.740 --> 00:19:32.969
So the problems can be solved just like that,

00:19:33.060 --> 00:19:34.993
if your attention is subtle.

00:19:35.281 --> 00:19:38.289
But if it is not the main the basic problem is

00:19:38.457 --> 00:19:40.457
that you cannot approach this.

00:19:41.361 --> 00:19:44.137
The approach to the problem is only possible

00:19:44.285 --> 00:19:46.130
if you are a subtle being.

00:19:46.232 --> 00:19:50.200
If you are not a subtle being you cannot approach any problem.

00:19:52.040 --> 00:19:55.461
So, to be subtle and to be there, to be Divine

00:19:55.598 --> 00:19:59.246
one has to understand the grossness that is covering you.

00:19:59.369 --> 00:20:00.852
Through Kundalini you can

00:20:00.955 --> 00:20:04.410
because you can raise your Kundalini, see where it is hanging.

00:20:04.534 --> 00:20:07.131
“Now it’s very heavy here. It’s like a stone here.

00:20:07.245 --> 00:20:08.867
It’s thumping here.

00:20:09.024 --> 00:20:10.983
It’s doing all these things.”

00:20:11.086 --> 00:20:13.466
Now, it’s a very gross way of looking at it,

00:20:13.568 --> 00:20:16.357
very gross way of looking at it. It is suggesting to you,

00:20:16.437 --> 00:20:17.437
something.

00:20:17.543 --> 00:20:22.030
So what you have to do is to see for yourself now, at Sahasrara,

00:20:22.121 --> 00:20:24.721
that’s the place for Somebody we know.

00:20:25.057 --> 00:20:28.577
Then you just sit down and say, “Now what have I done?

00:20:28.866 --> 00:20:30.723
Why this problem?

00:20:31.641 --> 00:20:35.867
If I have done anything like that, please forgive me!”

00:20:36.015 --> 00:20:39.019
It works out. It’s a simple way.

00:20:39.152 --> 00:20:41.613
But first of all, foremost thing, is that,

00:20:41.756 --> 00:20:43.480
what is the substance you gave me?

00:20:43.582 --> 00:20:47.294
Is it a subtle substance that’s speaking or the gross one?

00:20:48.941 --> 00:20:52.295
From which point are you speaking is the thing.

00:20:52.442 --> 00:20:55.070
Supposing you are speaking from that point

00:20:55.184 --> 00:20:58.156
where you are a governor general, everybody has to obey you!

00:20:58.304 --> 00:21:01.487
But if you are speaking from the point where you are a peon,

00:21:01.612 --> 00:21:03.478
nobody is going to obey you.

00:21:03.778 --> 00:21:06.157
So where is the attention is the thing.

00:21:06.249 --> 00:21:09.285
So mentally you have to work it out in your meditation.

00:21:09.400 --> 00:21:12.039
Now you sit down for meditation, all right,

00:21:12.152 --> 00:21:14.599
mostly trying to be thoughtlessly aware.

00:21:14.690 --> 00:21:18.482
But if there are thoughts you should try to keep it down by saying,

00:21:18.590 --> 00:21:22.356
“How fortunate that I have felt these vibrations, I felt it.

00:21:22.465 --> 00:21:24.525
And how happy I am about it!

00:21:24.617 --> 00:21:26.483
Now you get away all the negative thoughts!”

00:21:26.574 --> 00:21:27.996
That’s how you can fight it out.

00:21:28.059 --> 00:21:32.013
Now whatever you do will lead you to Sahaja, not before.

00:21:32.184 --> 00:21:34.811
Before Realisation it has got no meaning, it was a dead car

00:21:34.937 --> 00:21:37.976
standing there, but now the car has started moving.

00:21:38.088 --> 00:21:41.022
And whatever you do whatever you try,

00:21:41.135 --> 00:21:43.556
it will make you subtler and subtler.

00:21:43.660 --> 00:21:46.310
Simple things like declaration that,

00:21:46.424 --> 00:21:49.880
“Yes, I am going to do this! I have decided to do it.”

00:21:50.063 --> 00:21:53.305
Put your mind to positive thinking: What are we going to do?

00:21:53.420 --> 00:21:56.720
How are we going to do it? How are we going to work it out?

00:21:56.841 --> 00:21:59.313
You will be surprised how the things will come.

00:21:59.392 --> 00:22:02.656
But normally our habits are for our gross problems.

00:22:04.556 --> 00:22:07.524
Now I would say Bombay Sahaja Yogis are

00:22:07.638 --> 00:22:10.038
quite developed they are quite good

00:22:10.133 --> 00:22:12.711
but still sometimes they really tumbled down very badly.

00:22:12.813 --> 00:22:15.561
This time I thought they were a little bit proud

00:22:15.679 --> 00:22:18.094
than anything else because Delhi people were not so good at

00:22:18.197 --> 00:22:20.949
things and they had to come and do it.

00:22:21.108 --> 00:22:23.872
And I think that Bombay people did feel that they were

00:22:23.974 --> 00:22:28.237
sort of lending a hand to Delhi people. It happened.

00:22:28.657 --> 00:22:33.487
But then they found themselves quite low

00:22:33.601 --> 00:22:37.698
and and all of them Humpty Dumpties sitting down there!

00:22:37.809 --> 00:22:40.029
You see, so it can happen.

00:22:40.120 --> 00:22:41.922
So anyone who feels that,

00:22:42.024 --> 00:22:44.790
“I have achieved everything!” or, “I have reached everything!”

00:22:44.892 --> 00:22:46.798
can have a Humpty Dumpty fall.

00:22:46.924 --> 00:22:49.710
Because it was so beautifully played, you see.

00:22:49.858 --> 00:22:52.815
I'll tell you what happened: They came down

00:22:52.996 --> 00:22:56.708
and then in the Old Delhi we had no place to stay properly

00:22:56.874 --> 00:22:59.774
so I said, “All right, you arrange my place in the guesthouse

00:22:59.888 --> 00:23:01.702
and the boys can stay in the boys hostel

00:23:01.804 --> 00:23:03.639
and the girls can stay in the girls hostel.”

00:23:03.765 --> 00:23:05.771
“All right it can be done.”

00:23:06.383 --> 00:23:08.773
So then the gross thing came out.

00:23:08.909 --> 00:23:10.868
So one of the persons said that,

00:23:10.970 --> 00:23:13.486
“You see but the food in that boys hostel is full of oil

00:23:13.578 --> 00:23:18.033
and this and how can we eat there?”

00:23:20.277 --> 00:23:23.474
And I didn’t know about it, nobody told me.

00:23:23.656 --> 00:23:26.375
And then they had to arrange it with somebody

00:23:26.466 --> 00:23:28.867
and they had to suddenly purchase all the food

00:23:28.947 --> 00:23:32.416
and everything and then to arrange a cook and these things.

00:23:32.540 --> 00:23:36.063
And where they stayed was all full of bhoots!

00:23:36.437 --> 00:23:39.351
And they were all caught up in the head, terrible

00:23:39.454 --> 00:23:41.847
and this and that and they came to me.

00:23:41.951 --> 00:23:44.091
So they said, “Mother what has happened to us?

00:23:44.192 --> 00:23:46.449
We came all the way and this is what has happened.

00:23:46.530 --> 00:23:48.336
Now we are all vomiting and this and that.”

00:23:48.485 --> 00:23:50.946
I said, “Why? Where are you eating these days?

00:23:51.049 --> 00:23:53.101
Not in that oily place?”

00:23:53.486 --> 00:23:56.298
“No, we have our own cook we have our everything,

00:23:56.400 --> 00:23:58.645
but the problem is the house is full of bhoots and

00:23:58.759 --> 00:24:00.791
we are all finished with that!”

00:24:00.881 --> 00:24:02.795
So I said, “Who had asked you to suggest that?

00:24:02.910 --> 00:24:04.258
Can't you eat that food?

00:24:04.338 --> 00:24:06.256
So many thousands of boys are eating here.

00:24:06.367 --> 00:24:08.893
You are Sahaja Yogis you can't eat that food?

00:24:09.007 --> 00:24:11.340
Your attention is on the oily food

00:24:11.422 --> 00:24:14.176
what is so special about yourselves that you can't eat?

00:24:14.300 --> 00:24:17.608
I mean you should be able to eat even the stones.

00:24:17.688 --> 00:24:19.377
That’s what Sahaja Yoga is

00:24:19.445 --> 00:24:22.166
but you can’t eat the ordinary food that all so many

00:24:22.245 --> 00:24:23.978
thousands of boys are eating?

00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:26.811
And you wanted to stay away - such importance of yourself,

00:24:26.959 --> 00:24:30.287
so go ahead!” And it was all done by satanic forces.

00:24:30.392 --> 00:24:32.339
You should have thought once at least that,

00:24:32.442 --> 00:24:35.729
“Why are we wanting to go away from here that place?

00:24:35.854 --> 00:24:39.950
When where it is all organised, let us be here!” That is Sahaja.

00:24:40.604 --> 00:24:42.972
That part also they didn’t understand

00:24:43.052 --> 00:24:45.694
— discrimination also of what is Sahaja what is asahaja?

00:24:45.820 --> 00:24:47.983
Where are you Sahaja and where are you not,

00:24:48.087 --> 00:24:50.874
you should discriminate it. That point at least one should reach.

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:53.362
So the so called, the high, top class

00:24:53.453 --> 00:24:57.338
Sahaja Yogis fell down like that, and they felt very shy and bad.

00:24:57.428 --> 00:25:01.316
I said, “It’s all right, don't you worry.” But it’s a simple thing.

00:25:01.453 --> 00:25:02.785
It's a lesson now.

00:25:02.899 --> 00:25:06.017
Because you can overcome [the] food problem

00:25:06.130 --> 00:25:07.930
but what about the bhoots?

00:25:08.080 --> 00:25:09.679
Why should you go in with somebody,

00:25:09.770 --> 00:25:11.685
a person who has just come to Sahaja Yoga,

00:25:11.765 --> 00:25:13.796
and you don't know what sort of person he is?

00:25:13.897 --> 00:25:15.731
They said, “Mother, it's your Maya!”

00:25:15.848 --> 00:25:18.622
I said, “But what about you? You people were thinking that you are

00:25:18.690 --> 00:25:21.683
great and you are the greatest Sahaj Yogis ever born,

00:25:21.785 --> 00:25:24.685
and you are the topmost among all the worlds!

00:25:24.980 --> 00:25:26.576
So don’t think like this.”

00:25:26.725 --> 00:25:29.229
And this is what happened. You see, so it plays on you,

00:25:29.331 --> 00:25:31.798
just to test you and it works on you.

00:25:31.880 --> 00:25:35.959
So, ‘sahaja’ means whatever comes your way you take it, no doubt,

00:25:36.083 --> 00:25:39.904
but you do it yourself with positiveness. That is very necessary.

00:25:40.020 --> 00:25:42.580
That doesn’t mean that you go on accepting everything ‘sahaja’ :

00:25:42.637 --> 00:25:45.085
“The bhoots coming onto me, I’m accepting, everything

00:25:45.176 --> 00:25:46.627
coming onto me I am accepting.

00:25:46.696 --> 00:25:49.110
That is not the way it is Sahaja, that’s the point.

00:25:49.220 --> 00:25:52.627
When we start doing like that, then

00:25:52.797 --> 00:25:55.348
actually ‘sahaja’ what you will get is bhoots,

00:25:55.473 --> 00:25:57.649
and what you will get is all the negativity,

00:25:57.775 --> 00:26:01.343
and also you’ll get all the sickness, illness, everything.

00:26:01.593 --> 00:26:03.273
You have to be careful.

00:26:03.707 --> 00:26:06.823
So mentally you should be alert.

00:26:07.436 --> 00:26:09.702
Physically you should work it out.

00:26:10.020 --> 00:26:13.056
And physically there is another point:

00:26:13.181 --> 00:26:16.378
is that you must look after your bodies, physically,

00:26:16.469 --> 00:26:18.336
[it’s] very much necessary,

00:26:18.441 --> 00:26:20.686
because this body is the temple of God.

00:26:20.800 --> 00:26:22.933
It is definitely now the temple.

00:26:23.440 --> 00:26:28.416
It’s a shrine. See how beautiful a shrine you have got.

00:26:29.391 --> 00:26:31.724
And I love to reside in this place.

00:26:32.418 --> 00:26:35.678
Let it be so beautiful that God should reside in that.

00:26:35.803 --> 00:26:39.510
Beautiful it is. Look after your body, look after your hair,

00:26:39.612 --> 00:26:43.602
look after yourself. If you treat yourself there’s no harm.

00:26:43.726 --> 00:26:46.036
People might say that, “Why should I treat myself?

00:26:46.127 --> 00:26:47.918
I must take all the burdens on myself!”

00:26:48.021 --> 00:26:52.147
All these out of date ideas of sufferings are useless for Sahaj Yog

00:26:52.250 --> 00:26:55.946
Nobody has to suffer.  You have to be very, very healthy people.

00:26:56.060 --> 00:26:58.302
Like somebody said that, “Why is it that Ramkrishna

00:26:58.393 --> 00:27:00.336
Paramahansa did not cure himself?

00:27:00.444 --> 00:27:03.230
Because he did not know how to cure himself, first of all.

00:27:03.956 --> 00:27:08.180
But Ramkrishna said, “I want to take all the burdens on my head.”

00:27:08.265 --> 00:27:11.632
You don't get sick if somebody who is sick you do not get sick.

00:27:11.760 --> 00:27:14.456
But, the only thing is that, if you look after your body,

00:27:14.546 --> 00:27:17.595
you respect your body, then your body also respects you.

00:27:17.703 --> 00:27:20.920
You body understands! If you don’t care for your body,

00:27:21.073 --> 00:27:23.099
you neglect your body, then body also says,

00:27:23.202 --> 00:27:25.135
“All right I'll have my way!”

00:27:25.282 --> 00:27:27.694
So you have to look after your body.

00:27:27.806 --> 00:27:29.894
You have to know how to keep it all right.

00:27:30.018 --> 00:27:32.149
I think we should really write it down,

00:27:32.243 --> 00:27:34.736
all the things that are to be done to look after your body.

00:27:34.848 --> 00:27:38.436
That is very important, because in these modern

00:27:38.537 --> 00:27:42.015
times or modern society, of course, you have devised ways

00:27:42.140 --> 00:27:44.870
of comfort that you press here,

00:27:45.006 --> 00:27:46.865
then you get everything coming down,

00:27:46.968 --> 00:27:49.073
you press there and you get food inside your stomach

00:27:49.164 --> 00:27:50.580
and all that is there.

00:27:50.739 --> 00:27:55.102
Not everywhere this is! That is all comfort they call it

00:27:55.193 --> 00:27:58.015
but I call it lethargy, or can call it laziness.

00:27:58.110 --> 00:28:00.416
It is not going to give you good health.

00:28:00.530 --> 00:28:03.861
Good health is possible only if you understand the balancing

00:28:03.975 --> 00:28:06.004
and have every understanding about

00:28:06.095 --> 00:28:08.362
how the body acts and what happens to body:

00:28:08.465 --> 00:28:11.617
small, small things like hot and cool, cold and hot.

00:28:11.708 --> 00:28:13.856
This is very important for Sahaj Yoga.

00:28:13.970 --> 00:28:16.983
You see Sahaja Yogis have to be perfect,

00:28:17.709 --> 00:28:19.309
absolutely perfect.

00:28:19.693 --> 00:28:23.332
And you don’t have to do with the norms of the modern times that

00:28:23.435 --> 00:28:26.682
everybody should be thin and everybody should be absolutely

00:28:26.920 --> 00:28:31.977
a TB patient going down for some sort of beauty parade!

00:28:32.780 --> 00:28:36.133
You should be all very healthy people and impressive.

00:28:36.326 --> 00:28:39.070
Whenever you sit there people should literally

00:28:39.184 --> 00:28:40.984
be frightened of you that,

00:28:41.110 --> 00:28:43.710
“From where these wrestlers have come?”

00:28:45.780 --> 00:28:52.228
So this is the sign of attending to your health attending yourself

00:28:52.884 --> 00:28:54.751
and your mental health also.

00:28:54.881 --> 00:28:57.928
And that’s why I say that you [should] be that you careful as to

00:28:58.054 --> 00:29:00.649
what you read and what you see and what you hear

00:29:00.797 --> 00:29:02.701
and how much attention you pay to it.

00:29:02.781 --> 00:29:05.409
You see supposing now a person like David comes here:

00:29:05.489 --> 00:29:07.703
you pay too much attention to a man like that.

00:29:07.773 --> 00:29:09.538
Everything is filled with that,

00:29:09.595 --> 00:29:11.307
the whole atmosphere is talking about it.

